#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsMedia.php:62
msgid "Also, make sure to organize your media files sensibly. This is especially useful if you have a lot of media files."
msgstr "此外，請務必合理地組織您的媒體檔案。如果您有很多媒體檔案，這一點尤其有用。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourExport.php:68
msgid "Also, remember that if you transfer a lot of content, it can take up a lot of space. Make sure you have enough room in your workspace to store it!"
msgstr "此外，請記住，如果您傳輸大量內容，可能會佔用很多空間。請確保您的工作區有足夠的空間來存放！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUser.php:62
msgid "An Administrator can revoke rights from all users... including you! So, be cautious about whom you assign the \"Administrator\" role."
msgstr "管理員可以撤銷所有使用者的權限...包括您！因此，請謹慎指定「管理員」角色的使用者。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourProfile.php:50
msgid "And just like that, we're done with another page. Users bring life to your website but also pose certain risks. So be careful about who you give what rights to."
msgstr "就這樣，我們又完成了一個頁面。使用者為您的網站帶來了活力，但也帶來了一定的風險。因此，在賦予哪些人哪些權利時一定要謹慎。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:56
