#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiShop.php:85
msgid "How does it work?"
msgstr "它是如何工作的？"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiQuest.php:62
msgid "I would be thrilled if you could leave some feedback for my developers. It helps them improve me and better assist you in the future."
msgstr "如果您能為我的開發人員留下一些回饋意見，我會感到非常高興。這有助於他們改善我，並在未來更好地協助您。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourSiteHealth.php:56
msgid "If you click on the \"Report\" tab, you'll get a detailed breakdown of the technical aspects of your website. Take a look if you're in the mood to be completely baffled!"
msgstr "如果您點選「報告」標籤，您就會得到網站技術方面的詳細分解。如果您有心情完全摸不著頭腦，請看一看！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsPrivacy.php:62
msgid "If you're having trouble sleeping, consider reading the \"Policy Guide\" on privacy statements. It always puts me to sleep in seconds!"
msgstr "如果您失眠，請考慮閱讀隱私權聲明的 「政策指南」。它總是能讓我在幾秒鐘內入睡！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourImport.php:43
msgid "Import"
msgstr "匯入"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourImport.php:50
msgid "Importing content is handy when you want to transfer content from another website to here or restore a backup of your website."
msgstr "當您要將網站內容從其他網站轉移到這裡，或是還原網站備份時，匯入內容就非常方便。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:50
msgid "In \"All Posts\", you can view, organize, and manage all your posts at a glance. Additionally, you can start making new posts right from here!"
msgstr "在「所有文章」中，您可以一目了然地檢視、整理和管理所有文章。此外，您也可以從這裡開始發表新文章！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditCategory.php:67
msgid "In Summary"
msgstr "總結"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUsers.php:50
msgid "In the \"All Users\" page, you can see and manage all the users of your website."
msgstr "在「所有使用者」頁面中，您可以看到並管理網站的所有使用者。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourSiteHealth.php:44
msgid "In the \"Site Health\" page, you can check out the overall health of your website."
msgstr "在「網站健康狀況」頁面中，您可以檢查網站的整體健康狀況。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPlugins.php:62
msgid "In the Plugin Overview, you can see and manage all your installed plugins. Here, you can also easily activate or deactivate the plugins you're using."
msgstr "在「外掛程式總覽」中，您可以看到並管理所有已安裝的外掛程式。在這裡，您也可以輕鬆啟用或停用您正在使用的外掛程式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:98
msgid "In the content area, you can edit your contents... write texts, insert images, edit blocks. The sky's the limit with your creativity!"
msgstr "在內容區域，您可以編輯內容...撰寫文字、插入圖片、編輯區塊。您的創意無限！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:98
msgid "In the content part, you can edit your contents, write texts, insert images, and edit blocks. Unleash your creativity!"
msgstr "在內容部分，您可以編輯內容、撰寫文字、插入圖片和編輯區塊。釋放您的創意！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:86
msgid "In the settings bar, you can save and publish your page. Plus, you can switch between different screen modes like desktop, mobile, and tablet."
msgstr "在設定列中，您可以儲存和發佈您的頁面。此外，您還可以在桌面、手機和平板電腦等不同的螢幕模式之間切換。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:86
msgid "In the settings bar, you can save and publish your post. Plus, you can switch between different screen modes like desktop, mobile, and tablet."
msgstr "在設定列中，您可以儲存和發表您的文章。此外，您還可以切換不同的螢幕模式，例如桌上型電腦、手機和平板電腦。"

