msgid "Summary"
msgstr "概要"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:85
#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:43
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "標籤"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:68
msgid "Tags are a key part of Search Engine Optimization (SEO). They help search engines better understand and index the content of your posts."
msgstr "標籤是搜尋引擎最佳化 (SEO) 的關鍵部分。它們有助於搜尋引擎更好地理解和索引您的文章內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiQuest.php:43
msgid "Task Overview"
msgstr "任務概述"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourMedia.php:44
msgid "The \"Add New Media File\" page lets you upload fresh media like images, videos, or audio files to your media library."
msgstr "新增媒體檔案」頁面可讓您將圖片、視訊或音訊檔案等新媒體上傳至媒體素材庫。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourDashboard.php:68
msgid "The \"Admin Menu\" makes switching between different areas of your website a breeze. You can easily access one of these areas by clicking on a main menu item."
msgstr "管理選單」讓您輕鬆切換網站的不同區域。按一下主選單項，即可輕鬆存取其中一個區域。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:68
msgid "The \"Comment\" field displays the actual content of the comment left by a visitor on your website."
msgstr "評論」欄位會顯示訪客在您網站上留下的實際評論內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:80
msgid "The \"Date\" field indicates when the comment was left on your website."
msgstr "日期」欄位會顯示評論是何時在您的網站上留下的。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsDiscussion.php:44
msgid "The \"Discussion\" page deals with settings related to comments and discussions on your website."
msgstr "討論」頁面處理與網站上的評論和討論相關的設定。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemeEditor.php:44
msgid "The \"Edit Themes\" page allows you to modify the files of your theme."
msgstr "編輯主題」頁面可讓您修改主題的檔案。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsGeneral.php:50
msgid "The \"General\" page is the first page you see when you enter \"Settings\". Here, you can set your website's name, URL, timezone, and date format."
msgstr "一般」頁面是您進入「設定」後看到的第一個頁面。在這裡，您可以設定網站的名稱、URL、時區和日期格式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPlugins.php:50
msgid "The \"Installed Plugins\" page lets you manage the plugins you've already installed."
msgstr "已安裝外掛程式」頁面可讓您管理已安裝的外掛程式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsMedia.php:44
msgid "The \"Media\" page deals with the basic settings for managing media files on your website."
msgstr "媒體」頁面處理網站上管理媒體檔案的基本設定。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsPermalink.php:44
msgid "The \"Permalink\" page deals with settings for the URL structure of your website."
msgstr "Permalink」頁面處理網站 URL 結構的設定。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsPrivacy.php:44
msgid "The \"Privacy\" page is designed for managing your website's privacy policies."
msgstr "隱私權」頁面專為管理網站的隱私權政策而設計。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsReading.php:44
msgid "The \"Reading\" page allows you to set basic display settings for your website."
msgstr "閱讀」頁面可讓您設定網站的基本顯示設定。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemes.php:50
msgid "The \"Themes\" page lets you change the design of your website."
msgstr "主題」頁面可讓您變更網站的設計。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsWriting.php:44
msgid "The \"Writing\" page helps you with creating posts and articles."
msgstr "撰寫」頁面可協助您撰寫文章。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourDashboard.php:55
msgid "The Admin-Bar"
msgstr "管理列"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:74
msgid "The Author column shows who created the post. If there are multiple authors, it'll display their usernames."
msgstr "Author (作者) 欄會顯示誰建立了這篇文章。如果有多位作者，則會顯示他們的使用者名稱。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:56
msgid "The Overview Page lists all your posts. From here, you can easily create new posts and make quick edits to existing ones."
msgstr "總覽頁面會列出您所有的文章。在這裡，您可以輕鬆建立新文章，並快速編輯現有文章。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:62
msgid "The Post List shows you all your posts, along with key details like title, author, and publication date."
msgstr "貼文清單會顯示您所有的貼文，以及關鍵的詳細資訊，例如標題、作者和發表日期。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourDashboard.php:116
msgid "The Rundown"
msgstr "簡介"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:86
msgid "The Tags column lists the tags associated with your posts. Tags make it easier to find content on similar topics."
msgstr "標籤列會列出與您的文章相關的標籤。標籤可讓您更容易找到類似主題的內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:68
msgid "The Title column displays the titles of all your posts. Click on any title to edit the post and change its content."
msgstr "標題列會顯示您所有文章的標題。按一下任何標題可編輯文章並變更其內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:61
#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:61
msgid "The Toolbar"
msgstr "工具列"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiShop.php:62
msgid "The items you can equip me with are divided into categories. Check back often, as new items are continuously added!"
msgstr "您可以為我裝備的物品分為多個類別。請經常回來查看，因為新物品會不斷加入！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditCategory.php:62
msgid "The overview page not only shows all your categories but also their hierarchical relationships. Check out how often your categories are used in your posts."
msgstr "總覽頁面不僅會顯示您所有的類別，還會顯示它們的層級關係。查看您的分類在文章中的使用頻率。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourImport.php:56
msgid "The overview page shows a list of tools that can assist you in importing content. They vary depending on the plugins you have installed and your WordPress version."
msgstr "總覽頁面會顯示可協助您匯入內容的工具清單。它們會因您安裝的外掛程式和 WordPress 版本而異。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:62
msgid "The overview section shows all your created tags. You'll also see info on how often your tags are used in your posts."
msgstr "總覽部分顯示您建立的所有標籤。您也會看到您的標籤在文章中使用頻率的資訊。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPluginEditor.php:50
msgid "The same principles apply as with editing themes. On this page, you can make direct changes to the files of your plugins. You should have some programming knowledge if you're planning to work here."
msgstr "原則與編輯主題相同。在此頁面中，您可以直接變更外掛程式的檔案。如果您打算在此工作，您應該具備一些程式設計的知識。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:98
msgid "The search bar lets you look for specific pages, which is super handy if you have lots of them."
msgstr "搜尋列可讓您尋找特定的頁面，如果您有很多頁面，搜尋列會非常方便。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:92
msgid "The search function lets you look for specific comments based on keywords, usernames, email addresses, or other relevant info."
msgstr "搜尋功能可讓您根據關鍵字、使用者名稱、電子郵件地址或其他相關資訊來尋找特定的評論。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsDiscussion.php:50
msgid "The settings you choose here will impact how you interact with your visitors. For example, you can set conditions under which comments are allowed."
msgstr "您在此選擇的設定會影響您與訪客互動的方式。例如，您可以設定允許發表意見的條件。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsGeneral.php:56
msgid "The settings you establish here are really important as they form the foundation of your website. So, you should carefully review and set these settings."
msgstr "您在此建立的設定非常重要，因為它們構成您網站的基礎。因此，您應該仔細檢閱和設定這些設定。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:104
msgid "The text editor has loads of features, and I'm sure I forgot to explain half of them! Hope I at least gave you a good start."
msgstr "文字編輯器有許多功能，我肯定忘了解釋其中一半的功能！希望我至少能給你一個好的開始。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:104
msgid "The text editor has so many features, and I'm sure I forgot to explain half of them! I hope I at least gave you a good overview. Let's take a look at the next area."
msgstr "文字編輯器有許多功能，我肯定忘了解釋其中一半的功能！我希望我至少給了您一個很好的概述。讓我們來看看下一個區域。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:62
msgid "The toolbar offers features to build your post step by step. Add new block elements and undo changes. Wanna see how it works? Hit the ► button!"
msgstr "工具列提供逐步建立文章的功能。新增區塊元素並撤銷變更。想看看它是如何運作的嗎？按一下 ► 按鈕！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:62
msgid "The toolbar provides functions to help you build your page step by step. Here you can add new block elements and undo changes. Want to see how it works? Hit the ► button!"
msgstr "工具列提供的功能可協助您逐步建立頁面。您可以在此新增區塊元素，並撤銷變更。想看看它是如何運作的嗎？按一下 ► 按鈕！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:56
msgid "The top navigation gives you quick access to basic controls in the editor. It's split into the toolbar and the settings bar."
msgstr "頂部導覽可讓您快速存取編輯器中的基本控制。它分成工具列和設定列。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPost.php:56
msgid "The top navigation gives you quick access to essential controls in the editor. It's split into the toolbar and the settings bar."
msgstr "頂部導覽可讓您快速存取編輯器中的重要控制項。它分成工具列和設定列。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemes.php:49
msgid "Themes"
msgstr "佈景主題"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemes.php:68
msgid "There are also themes that are installed but not active. You can switch between them by activating an inactive theme, which would then change the design of your website accordingly."
msgstr "還有一些已安裝但未激活的主題。您可以透過啟動未啟用的主題在它們之間切換，這樣就可以相應地改變網站的設計。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPlugins.php:86
msgid "There are incredibly many plugins, and you'll find that there's a plugin solution for almost every problem!"
msgstr "外掛的數量多得令人難以置信，而且您會發現幾乎所有問題都有外掛解決方案！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:80
msgid "This column shows the date when the page was created or last edited."
msgstr "此列顯示頁面建立或最後一次編輯的日期。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:68
msgid "This column shows the titles of all pages. Click a title to edit the page and change its content."
msgstr "此欄顯示所有頁面的標題。按一下標題可編輯頁面並變更其內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:74
msgid "This column shows who created the page. For multiple authors, it'll display their names."
msgstr "此欄顯示誰建立了該頁面。對於多位作者，會顯示他們的姓名。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:62
msgid "This field lets you quickly see who left the comment. For registered visitors, their email address is also shown."
msgstr "此欄位可讓您快速查看誰留下了評論。對於註冊的訪客，他們的電子郵件地址也會顯示出來。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourTools.php:50
msgid "This is the \"Available Tools\" page. Here you'll find a list of tools that can help you manage your website."
msgstr "這是「可用工具」頁面。在這裡您可以找到可以幫助您管理網站的工具清單。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditCategory.php:44
msgid "This is the \"Categories\" page! These are super handy for organizing and structuring your content, making it easier for visitors to find relevant info."
msgstr "這是「類別」頁面！這些類別對於組織和結構化您的內容非常方便，讓訪客更容易找到相關資訊。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:44
msgid "This is the \"Tags\" page! Tags let you enhance your posts with additional keywords or phrases. That way, your content can be found and searched through easier!"
msgstr "這是「標籤」頁面！標籤可讓您使用額外的關鍵字或詞組強化您的文章。如此一來，您的內容就能更容易被搜尋到！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourTools.php:56
msgid "This is the overview page for available tools. Here, you can see and manage the tools available to you. They vary depending on the plugins you have installed and your WordPress version."
msgstr "這是可用工具的總覽頁面。在這裡，您可以查看和管理可用的工具。它們會因您安裝的外掛程式和 WordPress 版本而異。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:56
msgid "This is where you'll find a list of all the comments left by visitors on your website, including the comment text, the author's name, the post they commented on, and the date."
msgstr "在這裡您可以找到訪客在您網站上留下的所有評論清單，包括評論文字、作者姓名、所評論的文章以及日期。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPluginEditor.php:44
msgid "This page allows you to edit the files of your plugins."
msgstr "此頁面允許您編輯外掛程式的檔案。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourOptionsPrivacy.php:50
msgid "This page allows you to ensure that your website complies with privacy policies and legal requirements. There are also plugins available that provide additional support."
msgstr "此頁面可讓您確保網站符合隱私權政策和法律規定。也有提供額外支援的外掛程式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourDashboard.php:117
msgid "This page gives you a summary of everything – new posts, recent comments, and stats from across your website."
msgstr "此頁面提供您所有內容的摘要 - 新文章、最近的評論，以及整個網站的統計資料。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:50
msgid "This page is a key tool for engaging with your visitors. Here, you can respond to feedback and moderate discussions."
msgstr "此頁面是與訪客互動的重要工具。在這裡，您可以回應回饋和主持討論。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourErasePersonalData.php:50
msgid "This page is pretty much like the personal data export page. Here, you can delete a specific user's personal data."
msgstr "這個頁面跟個人資料匯出頁面差不多。在這裡，您可以刪除特定使用者的個人資料。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUser.php:50
msgid "This page is pretty self-explanatory. But be extra careful with assigning roles, as they determine the permissions a user has!"
msgstr "這個頁面很容易說明。但在指派角色時要格外小心，因為角色會決定使用者擁有的權限！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:62
msgid "This page overview gives you a good look at all the pages you've created. Plus, you can organize and manage them from here."
msgstr "此頁面總覽可讓您清楚瞭解您所建立的所有頁面。此外，您還可以從這裡整理和管理它們。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiQuest.php:44
msgid "This page, \"Tasks\", provides an overview of the tasks you've completed and those still awaiting your attention."
msgstr "任務」這一頁提供您已完成和仍在等待您處理的任務總覽。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:80
msgid "This shows the categories assigned to a post. Categories help organize content on your website in a structured way."
msgstr "這會顯示指定給文章的類別。類別有助於有條理地組織您網站上的內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:74
msgid "This shows which post the comment is referring to, helping you understand the context."
msgstr "這會顯示評論所指的文章，有助於您瞭解上下文。"

