#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:50
msgid "Unlike categories, which group posts into broad themes, tags give more specific details. They help you connect particular topics, keywords, or phrases to your posts."
msgstr "標籤與分類不同，分類可將文章歸類為廣泛的主題，而標籤則可提供更明確的細節。它們可以幫助您將特定主題、關鍵字或短語與您的文章連接起來。"

