msgstr "警告"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPlugins.php:44
msgid "We are currently in the submenu of the \"Plugins\" main menu item. Here, you can search for, install, and activate new plugins."
msgstr "我們目前在「外掛程式」主功能表項的子功能表中。在此，您可以搜尋、安裝及啟動新外掛程式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUsers.php:44
msgid "We're in the submenu that falls under the \"Users\" main menu item. Here, you can manage the users of your website."
msgstr "我們現在處於「使用者」主功能表項下的子功能表。在這裡，您可以管理網站的使用者。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:44
msgid "We're now exploring the submenu of the \"Pages\" main menu item. This is where you manage all your static content."
msgstr "我們現在要探索「頁面」主選單項目的子選單。這是您管理所有靜態內容的地方。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUpload.php:44
msgid "We're now in the submenu of the \"Media\" main menu item. This is where you manage all the media files you add to your posts or pages."
msgstr "我們現在進入「媒體」主功能表項的子功能表。在這裡您可以管理添加到文章或頁面的所有媒體檔案。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPage.php:44
msgid "We're now on the \"Add New\" page. Just let me know once you're done with the Gutenberg editor tutorial, and I'll show you around some more."
msgstr "我們現在在 「新增 」頁面。完成 Gutenberg 編輯器教學後，請告訴我，我會再帶您參觀一些地方。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourTools.php:44
msgid "We've just moved into the submenu of the \"Tools\" main menu item. This page provides additional functions and resources, especially for administrators. Let's take a quick look."
msgstr "我們剛進入「工具」主功能表項的子功能表。此頁面提供額外的功能和資源，特別是針對管理員。讓我們快速瞭解一下。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourDashboard.php:43
msgid "Welcome Aboard!"
msgstr "歡迎登船！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPost.php:43
msgid "Welcome to Posts"
msgstr "歡迎來到職位"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPluginInstall.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the \"Add New Plugin\" page. Here, you can search for, install, and activate new plugins."
msgstr "歡迎來到「新增外掛程式」頁面。在此，您可以搜尋、安裝和啟動新外掛程式。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUser.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the \"Add New User\" page. Here, you can add users and manage their roles."
msgstr "歡迎來到「新增使用者」頁面。在此，您可以新增使用者並管理他們的角色。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourImport.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the \"Import\" page. Here, you can import content from other websites or WordPress installations."
msgstr "歡迎來到「匯入」頁面。在這裡，您可以從其他網站或 WordPress 安裝匯入內容。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourProfile.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the \"Profile\" page. Let's keep it brief: here, you can edit your profile. And on we go!"
msgstr "歡迎來到「個人資料」頁面。讓我們簡單介紹一下：在這裡，您可以編輯您的個人檔案。我們繼續！"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourWapuugotchiShop.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the most entertaining page of all... My page! 😄 Well, it's not exactly essential, but it's fun! Let's take a look."
msgstr "歡迎來到最有趣的頁面...我的頁面😄 好吧，這並不完全是必要的，但它很有趣！讓我們來看看。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemes.php:44
msgid "Welcome to the submenu of the \"Appearance\" main menu item. This is where you can manage the appearance and visual presentation of your website."
msgstr "歡迎來到「外觀」主功能表項的子功能表。在這裡您可以管理網站的外觀和視覺呈現。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemeInstall.php:50
msgid "When you enter this page, you'll see a selection of the most popular themes. This is super handy since there are more than 10,000 themes to choose from."
msgstr "當您進入這個頁面時，您會看到最熱門的主題選擇。由於有超過 10,000 種主題可供選擇，因此這超級方便。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUsers.php:68
msgid "When you hover over a user, a menu appears. Here, you can edit or delete a user. Give it a try!"
msgstr "將滑鼠移至使用者上方時，會出現一個功能表。在這裡，您可以編輯或刪除使用者。試試看"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditComments.php:49
msgid "Why Comments?"
msgstr "為什麼要評論？"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourMedia.php:56
msgid "WordPress supports a bunch of file formats, including images (JPEG, PNG, GIF), videos (MP4, MOV, WMV), audio files (MP3, WAV), and even documents (PDF, DOC, PPT, etc.)."
msgstr "WordPress 支援多種檔案格式，包括圖片 (JPEG、PNG、GIF)、視訊 (MP4、MOV、WMV)、音訊檔案 (MP3、WAV)，甚至是文件 (PDF、DOC、PPT 等)。"

