msgstr "寫作設定"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPlugins.php:68
msgid "You also have the option to search for specific plugins. This is handy when you have many plugins installed."
msgstr "您也可以選擇搜尋特定的外掛程式。當您安裝了許多外掛程式時，這會非常方便。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourMedia.php:62
msgid "You can also add media files directly to your posts or pages while you're editing them. Just click the \"Add Media\" button in the editor."
msgstr "您也可以在編輯文章或頁面時，直接將媒體檔案加入文章或頁面。只要按一下編輯器中的「新增媒體」按鈕即可。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourUpload.php:62
msgid "You can also edit the details of your media here. Change file names, add extra information, or tweak the metadata."
msgstr "您也可以在此編輯媒體的詳細資料。變更檔案名稱、新增額外資訊或調整 metadata。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourThemes.php:80
msgid "You can also install new themes. Let's take a look at how to do that."
msgstr "您也可以安裝新的主題。讓我們來看看如何安裝。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditCategory.php:50
msgid "You can create new categories to group your posts thematically. This not only makes navigation a breeze but also boosts SEO, helping users find your website when they search."
msgstr "您可以建立新類別，以主題方式將文章分類。這不僅可以輕鬆導覽，還可以提升 SEO，幫助使用者在搜尋時找到您的網站。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPostTag.php:56
msgid "You can create tags that match the specific content of your posts. These can be single words or short phrases that reflect the main concepts or themes of the post."
msgstr "您可以建立符合文章特定內容的標籤。這些標籤可以是反映文章主要概念或主題的單字或短語。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourPluginInstall.php:62
msgid "You can filter by the most popular, latest, and recommended plugins here. This way, you can, for example, follow the favorites of other WordPress users."
msgstr "您可以在此按最流行、最新和推薦的外掛程式進行篩選。舉例來說，這樣您就可以追蹤其他 WordPress 使用者的最愛。"

#: inc/onboarding/data/TourEditPage.php:92
msgid "You can sort your pages by different criteria, like date. There are also filtering options to display specific types of pages, like drafts."
msgstr "您可以依日期等不同條件排序頁面。還有篩選選項可顯示特定類型的頁面，例如草稿。"

#: inc/quest/data/QuestContent.php:123
